Lets see How we can add Two values at one index
When the array is sorted --->
-------------------------------------------
We want to rearrange array in such way-->alternating min max -->we will get
-----------------------------------------
Dividend=divissor*quotient+remainder--->1
quotient=Dividend/Divisor
remainder=Dividend%Divisor

--------------------------------------------------
Using first we will fix the divisor
divisor=(max)+1
So that every value will remain as it is
------------------------------------------------
In the above problem
even-->max
odd-->min
----------------------------------------------
if(i%2==0) a[i]=a[max_ind]%divisor*divisor+rem(a[i))
if(i%2==1) a[i]=a[min_ind]%divisor*divisor+rem(a[i])
--------------------------------------------
At last in order to retirve the corect value
iterate over the array
a[i]/divisor;-->correct value
-----------------------------------------------
